// ============================================================
// 中文摘要
// ============================================================
#let abstract-zh = [
  本文档是复旦大学学位论文 Typst 模板的使用说明。该模板严格遵循《复旦大学博士、硕士学位论文规范（2024年10月修订版）》的要求，基于 Typst 排版系统开发，支持本科、硕士（学术学位/专业学位）和博士（学术学位/专业学位）学位论文的排版。

  模板采用模块化分层架构设计，提供了完整的封面、声明页、扉页、摘要、目录、正文、参考文献、附录和致谢等页面模板。支持盲审模式、双面打印、命令行参数覆盖等功能。参考文献格式符合 GB/T 7714—2015 国家标准。

  本文档通过具体示例展示了模板的各项功能和使用方法，包括章节标题设置、图表排版、数学公式、代码块、参考文献引用等常见排版需求，以帮助用户快速掌握模板的使用。
]

#let keywords-zh = ("Typst", "学位论文", "复旦大学", "论文模板", "排版")

// ============================================================
// 英文摘要
// ============================================================
#let abstract-en = [
  This document serves as the user guide for the Fudan University thesis template built with the Typst typesetting system. The template strictly follows the "Fudan University Doctoral and Master's Thesis Regulations (Revised in October 2024)" and supports the typesetting of undergraduate, master's (academic/professional), and doctoral (academic/professional) theses.

  The template adopts a modular layered architecture, providing complete page templates for covers, declaration pages, title pages, abstracts, table of contents, main text, references, appendices, and acknowledgements. It supports blind review mode, double-sided printing, and command-line parameter overrides. The reference format complies with the GB/T 7714-2015 national standard.

  This document demonstrates the template's features and usage through specific examples, including chapter heading settings, figure and table typesetting, mathematical formulas, code blocks, and reference citations, helping users quickly master the template.
]

#let keywords-en = ("Typst", "Thesis", "Fudan University", "Template", "Typesetting")
